title: Nayuta Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan, Japanese, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Asian, Korean
description: Small vegan food bar where you can find Vietnamese coffee, tea, water, juices, plus soup and other Korean and Japanese style food. Cakes and other house-made desserts sometimes available. Owner speaks Korean, Japanese, and English. Situated inside the market area - to access it from Busandaehak-ro, go before the crossroad through the porch, take the first small street left (where there are some shops and graffiti on a wall) and after a few metres left again, you are there. Address 부산광역시 금정구 장전 1동 155-17 장성시장.
